pan>1</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/wsseo\">wsseo</a></strong> &#160; <div><p>OP</p></div>&#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-24 10:31:10 +08:00\">12h 7m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>哎，截图太湖了，看不出来。</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17899123\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/d68d/4ce5/388401_normal.png?m=1748309303\" alt=\"adajoy\" data-uid=\"388401\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>2</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/adajoy\">adajoy</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-24 10:41:20 +08:00\">11h 57m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>字体不一样，右边经典微软雅黑</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17899128\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/1922/85b6/249152_normal.png?m=1664507231\" alt=\"tencentcloud\" data-uid=\"249152\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>3</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/tencentcloud\">tencentcloud</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-24 10:41:36 +08:00\">11h 56m ago</span>  &#160; <span><img src=\"/static/img/heart_20250818.png?v=c3415183a0b3e9ab1576251be69d7d6d\" width=\"14\" alt=\"❤️\"> 1</span>\n                    \n                    <p>您好，非常抱歉给您带来不好的体验。我们已关注到您反馈的文字清晰度问题，并已同步产研团队进行评估分析。感谢您的反馈。</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17899284\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/815f/9fae/187268_normal.png?m=1777124300\" alt=\"codehz\" data-uid=\"187268\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>4</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/codehz\">codehz</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-24 10:59:50 +08:00\">11h 38m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>就是类似那帮啥玩意都搞 mactype 的人搞的吧，试图“优化”windows 字体渲染，实际是将自己口味强加给所有人</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17899385\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/6ed4/9287/102526_normal.png?m=1784328520\" alt=\"Dream4U\" data-uid=\"102526\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>7</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/Dream4U\">Dream4U</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-24 11:12:24 +08:00\">11h 26m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>看到 Windows 这💩一样的字体就想笑</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17899393\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/cdca/41db/41900_normal.png?m=1711607036\" alt=\"icanfork\" data-uid=\"41900\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>8</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/icanfork\">icanfork</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-24 11:13:49 +08:00\">11h 24m ago</span>  &#160; <span><img src=\"/static/img/heart_20250818.png?v=c3415183a0b3e9ab1576251be69d7d6d\" width=\"14\" alt=\"❤️\"> 2</span>\n                    \n                    <p>@<a href=\"/member/shunia\">shunia</a> 舆情监控系统，v2ex 也被列为监控对象之一而已，最终会落到一个系统内部做工单处理</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17899468\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/f39f/cabd/660117_normal.png?m=1715408332\" alt=\"gloeaerris\" data-uid=\"660117\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>9</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/gloeaerris\">gloeaerris</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-24 11:23:41 +08:00\">11h 14m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>显示器分辨率太低 + windows 字体渲染老古董</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17899484\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/8a4414637f3fee85b6bafc1161d02dcf?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"ttnl\" data-uid=\"441486\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>10</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/ttnl\">ttnl</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-24 11:25:06 +08:00\">11h 13m ago</span>  &#160; <span><img src=\"/static/img/heart_20250818.png?v=c3415183a0b3e9ab1576251be69d7d6d\" width=\"14\" alt=\"❤️\"> 1</span>\n                    \n                    <p>用的 Noto Sans ，没做低分屏适配</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17899501\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/e21f44ced2f969deae0623383266ca58?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"gogogo2000\" data-uid=\"54931\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>11</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/gogogo2000\">gogogo2000</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-24 11:27:21 +08:00\">11h 11m ago</span>  &#160; <span><img src=\"/static/img/heart_20250818.png?v=c3415183a0b3e9ab1576251be69d7d6d\" width=\"14\" alt=\"❤️\"> 1</span>\n                    \n                    <p>右侧一眼雅黑，屎一样的字体由于有了 hinting 让很多人觉得很清晰</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17899554\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/3d7ed54b70b2187e3f2a56b97bbc3178?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"Stop\" data-uid=\"57147\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>12</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/Stop\">Stop</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-24 11:33:44 +08:00\">11h 4m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>windows 的字体渲染就是垃圾，在意字体的建议别用。</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17899632\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/5bdf/44ad/21529_normal.png?m=1732809027\" alt=\"fkdtz\" data-uid=\"21529\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>13</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/fkdtz\">fkdtz</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-24 11:44:09 +08:00\">10h 54m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>不知道是不是设置问题，之前用 codex 也类似，一台电脑上看着清晰锐利，另一台就发糊，调整的字体和对比度什么的就好了</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17899799\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/912d/2b1c/751_normal.png?m=1715405735\" alt=\"cst4you\" data-uid=\"751\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>15</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/cst4you\">cst4you</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-24 12:18:01 +08:00\">10h 20m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>hinting 能不能滚出 Windows</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17900655\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/avatar/3396/10b4/260546_normal.png?m=1779087929\" alt=\"liubaicai\" data-uid=\"260546\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>18</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/liubaicai\">liubaicai</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-24 15:16:05 +08:00\">7h 22m ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>之前把几乎所有 base vsc 的 ide 都下下来体验了下，codebuddy 是最丑的。。</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        \n    \n    \n    \n    \n\n    \n        \n        <div id=\"r_17902147\">\n        \n        <table>\n            <tr>\n                <td><img src=\"https://cdn.v2ex.com/gravatar/811727846dc41cb1b5a9d7072939524f?s=48&d=retro\" alt=\"xuejianxianzun\" data-uid=\"199550\"></td>\n                <td></td>\n                <td><p><span>21</span></p>\n                    \n                    <strong><a href=\"/member/xuejianxianzun\">xuejianxianzun</a></strong> &#160; &#160; &#160;<span title=\"2026-07-24 22:16:31 +08:00\">22 mins ago</span> \n                    \n                    <p>我的屏幕上还行，估计还是和屏幕像素密度有关，Noto 字体其实是更好看的，但是需要高分屏</p>\n                </td>\n            </tr>\n        </table>\n        </div>\n    \n    \n    \n    \n\n\n</div></DIV>